    'note.params':'<b>Note.</b> Marginal distributions of the four <strong>augmented-utility</strong> parameters (Choi, Lee &amp; Lim 2025, §5).<br><strong>c<sub>l</sub></strong>&thinsp;: lying cost — penalises <strong>literal lies</strong> (m&thinsp;≠&thinsp;θ, Sobel Def.&thinsp;3).<br><strong>c<sub>d</sub></strong>&thinsp;: deception cost — penalises <strong>belief distortion</strong> (Sobel Def.&thinsp;4).<br><strong>α</strong>&thinsp;: CRRA risk-aversion coefficient — composition-based from risk-type proportions.<br><strong>β</strong>&thinsp;: other-regarding (altruism) weight — Normal(0.1,&thinsp;0.3).<br><strong>Source distributions</strong>&thinsp;: c<sub>l</sub>, c<sub>d</sub> ~ LogNormal(μ, σ=1) where μ is the log-scale location parameter configurable via sidebar sliders; each subplot annotation shows the generating distribution and the observed sample mean (x̄).',
